"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Four men talk about the terrible conditions in the Ukraine war. Two of them say they saw soldiers being shot for not following orders. The men thought they were going to Russia for training as bodyguards but ended up on the front line.\",            \"english_title\": \"Men Discuss Ukraine War\",            \"translated_version\": \"Cuatro hombres hablan sobre las malas condiciones en la guerra de Ucrania. Dos de ellos dicen que vieron a soldados ser disparados por no seguir \u00f3rdenes. Los hombres pensaron que iban a Rusia para entrenar como guardaespaldas pero terminaron en la l\u00ednea de frente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hombres Hablan de la Guerra en Ucrania\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Events were held across Ukraine to remember four years since Russia started its full-scale invasion.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine Remembers Invasion\",            \"translated_version\": \"Se hicieron eventos en toda Ucrania para recordar cuatro a\u00f1os desde que Rusia comenz\u00f3 su invasi\u00f3n completa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ucrania Recuerda la Invasi\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Hundreds of people have been forced to leave their homes and many are missing in Juiz de Fora. Rescue operations are still happening.\",            \"english_title\": \"People Leave Homes in Juiz de Fora\",            \"translated_version\": \"Cientos de personas han tenido que dejar sus casas y muchos est\u00e1n desaparecidos en Juiz de Fora. Las operaciones de rescate todav\u00eda est\u00e1n pasando.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Personas Dejan Casas en Juiz de Fora\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two people died when a tree fell on their car during a big winter storm. The storm also delayed flights and left thousands without power.\",            \"english_title\": \"Winter Storm Causes Deaths\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos personas murieron cuando un \u00e1rbol cay\u00f3 sobre su coche durante una gran tormenta de invierno. La tormenta tambi\u00e9n retras\u00f3 vuelos y dej\u00f3 a miles sin electricidad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tormenta de Invierno Causa Muertes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The police chief is resigning a year before his term ends. This news came after a rebuttal.\",            \"english_title\": \"Police Chief Resigns Early\",            \"translated_version\": \"El jefe de polic\u00eda est\u00e1 renunciando un a\u00f1o antes de que termine su mandato. Esta noticia vino despu\u00e9s de una respuesta.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Jefe de Polic\u00eda Renuncia Temprano\"        }    ]}"